	('SORpYCf1DIATglvAo9Iqi', 'Missing Ninja', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJeD4uvHyV3OvUJQExAi0bGoIZDF74LqSnHRdp', '<p>A neighboring village has requested our help in locating a missing shinobi. This shinobi has highly classified intel on the runnings of the village, and if captured and information forced, then the imminent destruction of the village is possible. Locate the shinobi, dispatch or capture any opposition you come across, and if alive, escort the shinobi back to the village.</p>', '<p>Welcome back to the village! It\'s sad to hear of the death of the missing shinobi, but good job on eradicating the kidnappers!</p>', 'B', '40', NULL, 'mission', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 150, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 25000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 150, \"reward_prestige\": 150, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 150}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"gufPdtyugthhn3K1fUsV9\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJeD4uvHyV3OvUJQExAi0bGoIZDF74LqSnHRdp\", \"sector\": 423, \"latitude\": 8, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 8, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"WZ5dXNa_lVfy5qfOlNHYH\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"WZ5dXNa_lVfy5qfOlNHYH\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://uploadthing.com/f/56d865da-1b2a-4e08-b07c-c4b109d455a4__f719dc6b-a5cd-41e6-847c-b9ae21a6c59f.webp\", \"sector\": 423, \"latitude\": 3, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\"