	('Tz9SDNJflBROWcJCFuqQR', 'Shrine Cleaning Duty', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJjOFPwK4XzPI8f1v96qBot0Q3wsUp2nxu7SMb', '<p>Take on the task of cleaning the Shrine of Amaterasu in Shine Village. Retrieve standard cleaning tools from the village supply room and proceed to the shrine. Ensure all areas, including floors, altars, and statues, are thoroughly cleaned and free of dust. Once completed, report back to the mission desk for acknowledgment and reward.</p>\n', 'That\'s how you do it. Praise the sun!', 'D', '10', NULL, 'mission', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 222, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 10000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 10, \"reward_prestige\": 10, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 25}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"uY15CqAtt6AVWcV0hMpGh\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJjOFPwK4XzPI8f1v96qBot0Q3wsUp2nxu7SMb\", \"sector\": 83, \"latitude\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 14, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"Pick up the cleaning tools.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"DhzyTspmrbYnaO8kzwGuj\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"DhzyTspmrbYnaO8kzwGuj\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJjOFPwK4XzPI8f1v96qBot0Q3wsUp2nxu7SMb\", \"sector\": 83, \"latitude\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 3, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"Clean up the shrine.\", \"