	('sINO0vefJwkfHQ7xQlRqZ', 'Stolen hat', 'https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJQXYpkRjhzBPya1rwfCIqOTU0cV5xgsMeo3u2', '<p>A group of Silence Genin have stolen the Kage\'s hat while he slept. Your mission will be to aprehend the Genin, then vigorously obtain the information on where the hat is, afterwards, toss them off the mountain and rid yourself of the evidence.</p>', '<p>They believed they could fly.</p>', 'B', '40', NULL, 'mission', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 670, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 25000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 150, \"reward_prestige\": 150, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 150}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"PFG8mDjMA36ub6A8PqYlV\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://utfs.io/f/Hzww9EQvYURJQXYpkRjhzBPya1rwfCIqOTU0cV5xgsMeo3u2\", \"sector\": 293, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 15, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"8zOPgvyrtchmCXJgfTrsl\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"8zOPgvyrtchmCXJgfTrsl\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://uploadthing.com/f/c52882c3-74c1-48b7-9510-a0d9c6885a32_maddoctor-removebg-preview.webp\", \"sector\": 293, \"latitude\": 12, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 11, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"opponentAIs\": [{\"ids\": [\"T1QJXDrl8ar6rzyUn0Fne\"], \"number\": 1}], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \