	('3XSo3-RrLIqG1o0Ng-9DL', 'Balista - The Diamond Dragon', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJg36l8KVcU9cpECTimBdjaqbNn7vQsxGR1wLk', '<h1>🚨 EMERGENCY DISPATCH</h1>\n<h2>PRIORITY: S-CLASS THREAT — SIEGE PROTOCOL</h2>\n\n<p><strong>ATTENTION:</strong> All <strong>Kage-Level Shinobi</strong> & <strong>Master Weaponsmiths</strong></p>\n\n<h3>🛑 SUBJECT: Legendary Entity Manifestation</h3>\n<p><strong>Designation:</strong> <span style=\"color:#b9f2ff;\">BALISTA, THE DIAMOND DRAGON</span></p>\n\n<h3>📍 LOCATION</h3>\n<p>\n  Confirmed emergence from deep within the <strong>Dragon\'s Tooth Mountains</strong><br>\n  Sector: <strong>34</strong><br>\n  Current Movement: <strong>Eastward path of destruction</strong>\n</p>\n\n<h3>🧱 VISUAL DESCRIPTION</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Composition:</strong> Body appears to be a single, impossibly dense and flawless diamond. Unlike Aery, it is not crystalline—it\'s solid, opaque, and seemingly indestructible.</li>\n  <li><strong>Form:</strong> Less like a traditional creature, more akin to a living siege engine. Its body is bulky, reinforced, and armored with overlapping diamond plates resembling fortress walls.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>⚡ WEAKNESS (Unconfirmed)</h3>\n<p>A <em>very strange Genin</em> reported dealing damage using a <strong>lightning-infused stone weapon</strong>. Use this information at your own discretion.</p>\n', 'Seichi is saved once more. ', 'D', '80', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 50000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 1000000, \"reward_badges\": [\"l9TWCcGthbmj8Dk5wZb4q\"], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 10000, \"reward_prestige\": 10000, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 10000, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"reward_seichi_silver\": 5, \"reward_medical_experience\": 300}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"Zx2Br\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"rewa