	('6bZzBUYiIZGvthNUIezDp', 'Baby Diamond Spotted', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJcWwtPUSnxBpQqGNDcTHbLmYz8uXAl3oa54ti', '<h1>🚨 EMERGENCY DISPATCH</h1>\n<h2>PRIORITY: B-CLASS THREAT — URGENT RECOVERY & DAMAGE CONTROL</h2>\n\n<p><strong>ATTENTION:</strong> All <strong>JONIN</strong> & <strong>Specialized Barrier Corps</strong></p>\n\n<h3>🛑 SUBJECT:</h3>\n<p><strong>Displaced Juvenile Entity</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Designation:</strong> <span style=\"color:purple;\">DIAMOND WHELP</span></p>\n\n<h3>📍 LOCATION:</h3>\n<p>\n  Last seen tumbling through the foothills near the <strong>Great Stone Quarry</strong> in <strong>Sector 35</strong>.<br>\n  Its path is <strong>erratic</strong> but generally trending <em>downhill</em>.\n</p>\n\n<h3>💎 VISUAL DESCRIPTION:</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Size:</strong> Comparable to a small cart or large boulder.</li>\n  <li><strong>Weight:</strong> Extremely heavy for its size.</li>\n  <li><strong>Composition:</strong> Entire body is composed of perfectly formed <span style=\"color:purple;\">purple diamond</span>.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>⚠️ WARNING:</strong> These entities are traveling in <strong>groups of 3</strong>. Engage with caution and coordinate barriers accordingly.</p>\n', 'Seichi is saved once more. ', 'D', '20', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 25000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 100000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 1000, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 1000, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"reward_skillpoints\": 0, \"reward_hunter_items\": false, \"reward_seichi_silver\": 5, \"reward_gathering_items\": false, \"reward_hunter_items_ids\": [], \"reward_hunting_experience\": 0, \"reward_medical_experience\": 300, \"reward_village_membership\": \"NONE\", \"reward_crafting_experience\": 0, \"reward_gathering_items_ids\": [], \"reward_gathering_experience\": 0}, \"object