	('4j9W0N4Hba24NFffn3ToX', 'The Eggs have Hatched', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJOQ68r9VHevxIThUauQkGJEBY3D2cPqy8f5sp', '<h1>🚨 EMERGENCY DISPATCH</h1>\n<h2>PRIORITY: A-CLASS THREAT — WIDESPREAD CONTAINMENT</h2>\n\n<p><strong>ATTENTION:</strong> All <strong>Chūnin</strong> and <strong>Lesser Jōnin</strong> Response Teams</p>\n\n<h3>🛑 SUBJECT: Mass Hatching Event</h3>\n<p><strong>Designation:</strong> <span style=\"color:green;\">EMERALD WHELPS</span></p>\n\n<h3>📍 LOCATION</h3>\n<p>\n  Confirmed nest site: <strong>Hyuogaan Mountains</strong><br>\n  Sector: <strong>25</strong> — Coordinates: <strong>(15, 18)</strong><br>\n  Additional Sightings: <strong>Sectors 25, 26, and 61</strong>\n</p>\n\n<h3>🧱 VISUAL DESCRIPTION</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Composition:</strong> Juvenile forms of the S-Class Emerald Dragon. Crystalline emerald scales and obsidian claws.</li>\n  <li><strong>Size:</strong> Comparable to a large wolf or ninken. Oversized wings, erratic flight.</li>\n  <li><strong>Distinguishing Features:</strong> Semi-translucent scales; constantly shed glittering dust that accelerates plant growth on contact.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>🧠 BEHAVIORAL ANALYSIS</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Instinct-Driven:</strong> Lacking higher intelligence. Disoriented, reactive.</li>\n  <li><strong>Voracious Hunger:</strong> Consuming livestock, small animals, and even mineral-rich rocks. Extremely high metabolism.</li>\n  <li><strong>Unpredictable Aggression:</strong> Alternating between hiding and sudden chakra bursts when startled.</li>\n  <li><strong>Innate Chakra Use:</strong> Uncontrolled nature chakra breath; not focused — causes violent plant eruptions. Highly volatile.</li>\n</ul>\n', 'Seichi is saved once more. ', 'D', '1', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 25000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 100000, \"reward_badges\": [\"AUref1waFsuow1dRjI3xE\"], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 1000, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"r