	('0mCYDsFmXwDLwZPOta80M', 'The Trial of Five Blades', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJxuQXrTWZsq9k0Von5rUfP6OgQ2TyptCKHS4u', 'Long ago, the Five Blades of Balance were wielded by elemental champions to end Seichi’s Great Collapse. Their successors now meet once a decade for the Trial of Blades—except this year, one blade-bearer is missing… and another has been assassinated. You must restore balance to the sacred trial and stop a rogue element from tipping the world into chaos.', 'The Wind Blade Spirit bows, its form dissolving into a peaceful breeze. The balance is upheld, the rogue blades secured. You have proven yourself worthy and earned the respect of the remaining elemental guardians. The Trial is complete.', 'D', '1', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 10000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [{\"ids\": [], \"number\": 0}], \"reward_money\": 75000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 1000, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 1000}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"lYg00\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\\\"I am Mizuha. We are the guardians of the Five Blades of Balance. Our decennial trial was meant to renew the elemental pact, but it has been desecrated. Daichi, the Earth Blade bearer, has been murdered, his blade shattered. Kaen of the Fire Blade is missing, and I fear the worst. A rogue force is trying to steal this power. Will you help me restore the balance?\\\"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"The balance must be protected. I will help\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"FKhMC\"}, {\"text\": \"This is a fight between gods and legends. It is not my place.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"Qb8gH\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"UBCd3LNPSLRU0bwbjaA2k\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"3gPEvcVkZ0ND1SF8slfdx\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"FKhMC\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You survey the scene. The ground is stained where Daichi fell, and the legendary Earth Blade lies in pieces on the stone floor, its power leaking into the earth like a poison.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Pick Up Item\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"DEPUf\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"UBCd3LNPSLRU0bwbjaA2k\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"DEPUf\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The ground trembles violently beneath your feet. The blade’s rage still lingers in these shards. Mizuha points to a trail of scorched earth leading away from the arena\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"That is Kaen\'s mark. Follow it. Find him\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"HyGW1\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"UBCd3LNPSLRU0bwbjaA2k\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"HyGW1\", 