ation... it was all to wake her up. She\'s coming for the final blade!\\\" Kika points toward the highest mountain peak before collapsing.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Ignore Kika\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"dlVgC\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"UpWui8mKSMsPX2OLEpOSI\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"dlVgC\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJxuQXrTWZsq9k0Von5rUfP6OgQ2TyptCKHS4u\", \"sector\": 20, \"latitude\": 8, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 6, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"The wind howls with unnatural fury. On the summit altar, the air itself begins to twist and solidify, forming a graceful, shimmering figure made of pure, cutting wind—the Wind Blade Spirit, awakened and enraged.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"Byqd-\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"vwUNUpKBfVpQfDy7hf9G-\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"Byqd-\", \"task\": \"start_battle\", \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"This is the final trial. Face the awakened Wind Blade Spirit and pacify its rage to restore elemental harmony.\", \"opponentAIs\": [{\"ids\": [\"fWxIoIf0M7EKffl-1BkVa\"], \"number\": 1}], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badge