	('_vil1aaMUxAuWCsOk9xHJ', 'Whispers of the Shining Sand', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJvC7ny2EmSnXwslYEpV1yOeNL8gMtqhjPdf36', 'You have come to the sun-drenched village of Shine seeking to understand the divine power of Amaterasu. The wise oracle, Sunstone, has agreed to guide you, but only if you can pass the trials of fire and wind, and uncover a shadowy conspiracy that threatens to extinguish the village\'s sacred light from within.\n', 'The Mirage Master dissolves into sand, his conspiracy shattered. You return to Sunstone, the truth revealed and the village safe. The oracle looks at you, his eyes filled with a new respect. \"You have faced the trials and exposed the darkness. Amaterasu\'s light shines brightly within you. You are always welcome in Shine, champion.\"\n', 'D', '1', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 0, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"id0-B\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Welcome, traveler. Amaterasu has guided you here. But knowledge of her blessing is not easily earned. A darkness gathers on the horizon. To prepare, you must first understand our origins. Seek out the \'Singing Sands\', a sacred dune, and listen to its song. It will reveal the first verse of the Sunstone Prophecy.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Go To the Temple\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"V5fSH\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"vy4fC-F3dV888Sj_Lm2DO\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"V5fSH\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJvC7ny2EmSnXwslYEpV1yOeNL8gMtqhjPdf36\", \"sector\": 73, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 6, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"d_NU1\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"vy4fC-F3dV888Sj_Lm2DO\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"d_NU1\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You reach the dune, and a haunting melody fills the air. The wind swirls, creating images in the sand of sun-baked shinobi and a radiant figure descending from the heavens. The first verse of the prophecy echoes in your mind:\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"From the heart of the desert, a prayer took flight, Amaterasu heard, and blessed the fading light. With wind and with fire, their spirits took flame, To guard the Shining Dunes, and carve their lasting name.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"Arr4t\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"vy4fC-F3dV888Sj_Lm2DO\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", 