	('hPoOuObNVVe3HPySDSPWx', 'The Tale of Goah Way: An Unwelcome Shadow', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJcAaQmcSnxBpQqGNDcTHbLmYz8uXAl3oa54ti', 'Goah Way, a peaceful wandering sage, is enjoying the sights of a bustling town. However, as dusk falls, he takes a shortcut through a dimly lit alley and finds his path blocked by a malicious ninja with sticky fingers. Guide Goah through this perilous encounter.\n', 'You made it back to your lodging, shaken but safe. The experience was frightening, but it has reinforced your resolve. The world is full of shadows, but your path is to praise the sun. The journey continues, now with a valuable lesson in vigilance.', 'D', '1', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 10000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 75000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 1000, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 1000}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"xK4o7SpoD-836g31OsRCl\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The day was wonderful, filled with new sights and friendly faces. But as the sun sets, you decide to take a shortcut back to your lodging through a quiet alleyway. The feeling of being watched has been nagging at you all day...\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Walk Through the Ally\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"r05q5RmGe8Ng0ka2bEqhI\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"cYu6VwVX55m6uq1oxlWc1\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"j4tEoLtefH12sZwZY6MF-\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"r05q5RmGe8Ng0ka2bEqhI\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJcAaQmcSnxBpQqGNDcTHbLmYz8uXAl3oa54ti\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"Head through the narrow alleyway.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"KRYcExWO4Y0yPUgo3MaMp\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"xSuCTLGL_YqzCCrifDlFM\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"KRYcExWO4Y0yPUgo3MaMp\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"A figure steps from the shadows, blocking your path. His masked face and malicious eyes leave no doubt as to his intentions. \\\"Well, well, what do we have here?\\\" he sneers. \\\"Paper-thin arms and a heavy-looking bag. Today must be my lucky day. Hand over your valuables, and I might let you walk away.\\\"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"I will not. You\'ll have to take them from me.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"ilbziKX-8I_8PqVkI0PST\"}, {\"text\": \"Look for an opening to escape.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"WZqVCtYEVsNpwrqvYW_e0\"}, {\"text\": \"(Give Up) \\\"Fine, take them. Just don\'t hurt me.\\\" \", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"rIHdAc6XdNwU3DadbgDix\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"xSuCTLGL_YqzCCrifDlFM\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"HgT0DKfi3pXjFzwc1U0v4\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"ilbziKX-8I_8PqVkI0PST\", \"task\": \"start_battle\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 7, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"Brave words for a man who looks like he\'d lose a fight to a strong breeze!\\\" He lunges, his blade flashing!\", \"opponentAIs\": [{\"ids\": [\"l-QeI1-lml0SMiEGL2qIh\"], \"number\": 1}], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fled from the opponent\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"51rhPGRZ_R8B1iYR5LgO5\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"xSuCTLGL_YqzCCrifDlFM\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"HgT0DKfi3pXjFzwc1U0v4\"], \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": true}, {\"id\": \"WZqVCtYEVsNpwrqvYW_e0\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The ninja lunges! As you dodge, you notice a glimmer of light reflecting off a nearby window. You remember the small, reflective disc a merchant gave you earlier. This could be your chance!\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"(Use Disc) Fling the reflective disc at the ninja\'s face\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"og35VaP09YTJIc8-DL4NE\"}, {\"text\": \"(Hesitate) \\\"I don\'t know... maybe I should just fight.\\\"\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"ilbziKX-8I_8PqVkI0PST\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"xSuCTLGL_YqzCCrifDlFM\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"HgT0DKfi3pXjFzwc1U0v4\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"rIHdAc6XdNwU3DadbgDix\", \"task\": \"fail_quest\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 7, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \" The ninja\'s blade is too fast. You fall, and he rifles through your belongings, taking everything of value. \\\"Should\'ve just praised the sun from your own backyard, old man,\\\" he sneers before melting back into the shadows, leaving you with nothing but scrapes and wounded pride.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"xSuCTLGL_YqzCCrifDlFM\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\"}, {\"id\": \"51rhPGRZ_R8B1iYR5LgO5\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJ2HmArGBnMXlcRpYmJ5do0zKw4Qx6PVEtBa9b\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"opponentAIs\": [{\"ids\": [\"l-QeI1-lml0SMiEGL2qIh\"], \"number\": 1}], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fled from the opponent\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"og35VaP09YTJIc8-DL4NE\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"xSuCTLGL_YqzCCrifDlFM\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"You manage to land a lucky blow, knocking the ninja off balance. He stumbles back, surprised by your tenacity, giving you a chance to flee. \", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": true, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"og35VaP09YTJIc8-DL4NE\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"With a flick of your wrist, you send the disc flying. It catches the last rays of sunlight, creating a brilliant flash that blinds the ninja! \\\"Agh! My eyes!\\\" he curses. You don\'t waste a second, turning and sprinting down the alley.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Run\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"QYkWH2kLsp_OuUqas5SEp\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"xSuCTLGL_YqzCCrifDlFM\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"QYkWH2kLsp_OuUqas5SEp\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJcAaQmcSnxBpQqGNDcTHbLmYz8uXAl3oa54ti\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 4, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 8, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"The ninja is recovering quickly! You hear his footsteps pounding the pavement behind you. You spot a decrepit building with a door slightly ajar. Hide inside!\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"NHXZP5QzqKWrS6y9N8w3r\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"G3UTBsuk1IA3_3p8mS8o7\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"NHXZP5QzqKWrS6y9N8w3r\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 4, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 8, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You slip inside, pulling the door shut as quietly as possible. Holding your breath, you listen as the ninja\'s footsteps approach, pause right outside, and then continue on, followed by a frustrated curse. You are safe.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"You are Safe\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"Ydfw0t3_S1UyrBmWLO89W\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"G3UTBsuk1IA3_3p8mS8o7\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"Ydfw0t3_S1UyrBmWLO89W\", \"task\": \"win_quest\", \"sector\": 33, \"latitude\": 4, \"longitude\": 8, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You made it back to your lodging, shaken but safe. The experience was frightening, but it has reinforced your resolve. The world is full of shadows, but your path is to praise the sun. The journey continues, now with a valuable lesson in vigilance.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"G3UTBsuk1IA3_3p8mS8o7\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\"}], \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": []}', '0', '2025-06-19 01:57:42.390', '2025-06-19 01:57:42.390', NULL, NULL, '1', '100', NULL, '3', '1', NULL, 'none', 'NONE', 'NONE', NULL),
	('K-Jzp32ZvJaXeunZFQtTa', 'The Serpent\'s Shadow', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJFDUsr5G2iOewJtjGzvNcmEX3TBnoSfMDZPH4', 'The air in Ryokuchi Village is thick with suspicion. Jin, the son of the powerful Stonefang clan\'s elder, is missing. The Stonefang clan blames their rivals, the secretive Whisperleaf clan. Hired as a neutral investigator, you must find the boy and uncover the truth before the village tears itself apart in a civil war', 'You return to the village square with Jin, safe and sound, and the true kidnappers in tow. The brewing war between the Stonefang and Whisperleaf clans is averted. Both leaders, humbled and grateful, thank you for your wisdom and skill in navigating their village\'s darkest hour.\n', 'D', '1', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 30000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 150000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 1000, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 1000}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"IJyO9\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The situation is... tense. Elder Kento of the Stonefang is convinced the Whisperleaf abducted his son, Jin. Matriarch Akari of the Whisperleaf claims they\'re being framed. Where will you begin? Every moment counts\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"I\'ll speak with the victim\'s father, Elder Kento.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"ODdSv\"}, {\"text\": \"I\'ll hear the denial from Matriarch Akari herself\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"OvoDF\"}, {\"text\": \"I\'ll start at the scene of the crime. Evidence doesn\'t lie\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"1KZky\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"-_GzzglIj16cXpO89bW-0\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"GX-3Nv7HaANz-qrR9Ki2i\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"ODdSv\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJFDUsr5G2iOewJtjGzvNcmEX3TBnoSfMDZPH4\", \"sector\": 88, \"latitude\": 6, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 6, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"nzNtr\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"1Qy5n4L2T5ZGl6czENLNw\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"OvoDF\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJFDUsr5G2iOewJtjGzvNcmEX3TBnoSfMDZPH4\", \"sector\": 88, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 9, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"_zKYl\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"5iAnJgfpXYsXjhuqFcNAr\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"1KZky\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJFDUsr5G2iOewJtjGzvNcmEX3TBnoSfMDZPH4\", \"sector\": 87, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"_2DGv\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"RxYPD9eCLGVIT7TjypurY\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"nzNtr\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"They took him! The Whisperleaf cowards stole my son! You\'ll find nothing on his patrol route but their planted evidence. Go see for yourself!\\\"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Check out the Route\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"1KZky\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"1Qy5n4L2T5ZGl6czENLNw\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"5fAKldtk8H__-6yObhrJK\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"_zKYl\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"This is a frame job. If we wanted to strike, we wouldn\'t leave such an obvious trail. Go to the patrol route. Look for evidence that is too perfect. The truth is there, if you have the wisdom to see it\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Head to the Patrol Route\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"1KZky\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"5iAnJgfpXYsXjhuqFcNAr\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"hDLuWEtxpMZHbVGJbDLnZ\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"_2DGv\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 87, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You arrive at the cliffs and find signs of a struggle. Searching the area, you find two key pieces of evidence: a small, black Whisperleaf Poison Dart and a Torn Stonefang Banner snagged on a rock.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"This dart is the key. I should get it analyzed.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"lXARZ\"}, {\"text\": \"This banner seems too convenient. I\'ll examine it closer.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"ZN3qr\"}, {\"text\": \"(Accuse) \\\"The dart is proof enough. I\'m confronting Matriarch Akari.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"J5tHU\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"RxYPD9eCLGVIT7TjypurY\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"lXARZ\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJFDUsr5G2iOewJtjGzvNcmEX3TBnoSfMDZPH4\", \"sector\": 88, \"latitude\": 8, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 8, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"The dart is coated in a strange substance. Take it to the village apothecary for analysis.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"MWwZq\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"scRbEgksROXJSNeqZ361Z\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"ZN3qr\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 87, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You examine the banner scrap. The tear is too clean, almost deliberate. More importantly, the mud caked on it is dark and silty, completely different from the reddish clay of the cliffs. This mud is from the riverbank. The evidence was planted.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Head To the Riverside\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"4CK9C\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"MWwZq\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"Ah, a Whisperleaf tranquilizer dart. A classic. But... wait.\\\" He sniffs it. \\\"The floral base is wrong. This is a cheap knock-off, made to look like their work. Sloppy. I heard rumors of some Ronin with a poor grasp of alchemy operating out of the old river caves..\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Head to Caves\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"4CK9C\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"scRbEgksROXJSNeqZ361Z\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"oOuVp1xcBJ1T5IBON8N_j\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"4CK9C\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJFDUsr5G2iOewJtjGzvNcmEX3TBnoSfMDZPH4\", \"sector\": 87, \"latitude\": 1, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 4, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"IAjlC\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"-NNXpIOj_vKn9PegKDivm\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"IAjlC\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 87, \"latitude\": 1, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 4, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You find a hidden Ronin camp. You overhear them talking. \\\"The ransom note is ready. Once the clans go to war over the boy, no one will notice us slipping away with the gold.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Start Battle\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"Ln3uG\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"-NNXpIOj_vKn9PegKDivm\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"c0sZV9WdOVbrE9zP-7kPe\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attacke