ption\": \"You present Jin and the captured ronin to the stunned clan leaders. The plot is revealed, and the imminent civil war is averted. Kento and Akari exchange a look of shared, humbled relief. \\\"You have saved our village,\\\" Akari says. \\\"You have our gratitude,\\\" Kento adds, bowing his head.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Mission Success\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"xvmQP\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"-_GzzglIj16cXpO89bW-0\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"5fAKldtk8H__-6yObhrJK\", \"hDLuWEtxpMZHbVGJbDLnZ\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"J5tHU\", \"task\": \"fail_quest\", \"sector\": 87, \"latitude\": 5, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\"}, {\"id\": \"xvmQP\", \"task\": \"win_quest\", \"sector\": 88, \"latitude\": 8, \"longitude\": 10, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\"}], \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": []}', '0', '2025-06-26 02:00:43.144', '2025-06-26 02:00:43.144', NULL, NULL, '1', '100', NULL, '3', '1', NULL, 'daily', 'NONE', 'NONE', NULL),
	('iqDcoYVBfL-49itpVd4b-', 'Roots of Renewal', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJugfSAsCyJLoOFkrcn4gxSwCfEQ9eMNXZlG8b', 'Something stirs deep within Seichi — not in the skies, nor the oceans, but beneath the old trees that whisper louder than wind. In the place where Konoki once stood proud, the ground does not forget. Its silence is not stillness. It listens. It breathes. It waits.\n\nThe forest has grown strange since its fall — not cursed, not corrupted, but alive in a way few understand. Beneath its roots hums an energy older than any village, deeper than any bloodline. They say its heart has turned to fire — not the blaze of destruction, but something tempered, something sacred. The warmth of renewal. The burn of truth. The echo of choices made and never unmade.\n\nThere’s talk of a grove near where Sector 300 gives way to deeper oakland. Just past the winding footpaths and to the southeast of where Konoki’s shrine once stood, the oaks thicken — eight great trees in a ring, ancient and untouched. Locals call it “the 3-0 gate” for how it lies where old patrol routes once crossed. You’ll know it when the air feels still and the leaves seem to listen.\n\nThis is not a mission. It is a trial. And the path through it will not be marked by force, but by the roots you choose to grow.\n\nIf your heart knows fire, and your hands still seek peace, then the forest will know you. And you may yet leave changed.', 'You walked a path most shinobi never attempt — one of self-control, not force. The forest does not cheer for you. It simply grows.', 'D', '1', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 7000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 250000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 500, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 750, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"reward_seichi_silver\": 5, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"MDZmQ\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJugfSAsCyJLoOFkrcn4gxSwCfEQ9eMNXZlG8b\", \"sector\": 308, \"latitude\": 13, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 1, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"The forest awaits your arrival\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": true, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"pzuh3\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"sAlHS9F6K0xXxFLH0Vuee\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"This place isn’t where Konoki began… but maybe where it begins again.\", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, {\"id\": \"pzuh3\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The wind carries no words, and yet you hear her. A voice, low and distant, curls into your thoughts like smoke through branches.  “Have you looked within, traveler? Before the forest may know you, you must know yourself.”  No form appears. Just warmth, and waiting.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Yes.. I Have looked, and i am still looking\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"JxZfn\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"sAlHS9F6K0xXxFLH0Vuee\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"The whisper fades, but the feeling of being watched does not.\", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, {\"id\": \"JxZfn\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The wind stills. The birds do not sing. Her voice arrives again — softer now, not distant but close, curling like mist against your skin.  “If you know thyself, then step forward. But if your heart hides in shadow… if you fear what may root inside you… then turn back now. The forest does not suffer lies, even the ones we tell ourselves.”  The path ahead narrows between tall oaks, their bark charred with the memory of flame. The ground feels older than it should — and quieter than any place with life. Something is waiting. Not just to see you… but to know you.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Step into the forest\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"mldBk\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"sAlHS9F6K0xXxFLH0Vuee\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"The woods close behind you like a closing eye. There is no going back now.\", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, {\"id\": \"mldBk\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \" Her voice no longer whispers. It speaks — solemn, distant, yet weighed with memory.  “Long ago, we lost much. Not to blade, but to flame. All that stood was turned to smoke, and all we carried was our faith. But even that burns under doubt.”  The energy in the forest shifts — not violent, but restless.  “The spirits are no longer at peace. They do not hate… but they hurt. Betrayed. Confused. Find the heart of their sorrow. Go where flame once touched root.”\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Continue making your way through the forest\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"qtt2J\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"The air thickens with memory. The clearing awaits.\", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, {\"id\": \"qtt2J\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJugfSAsCyJLoOFkrcn4gxSwCfEQ9eMNXZlG8b\", \"sector\": 308, \"latitude\": 7, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 3, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"Ash feeds soil. From this, something new may grow.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"scg_f\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"HumC4xPuif2La1N-WvGx9\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"You reach the Charred Clearing of the Forest\", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, {\"id\": \"scg_f\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The silence afterward is heavy — not empty, but full of longing. Then her voice returns, softer now, touched with sadness.  “We grew once. Tall. Strong. Wise. But the fire beneath our bark has never cooled. The forest cannot reclaim itself while that pain lives still in root and spirit alike.”  A breeze circles you gently, cool and reverent. Her voice fades like smoke between branches — not dismissed, not denied, only gone. The woods return to silence. She does not speak again.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"I will do what i must.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"nFnjt\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"HumC4xPuif2La1N-WvGx9\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"The air lifts. A breeze passes, carrying the scent of new life. \", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, {\"id\": \"nFnjt\", \"task\": \"pvp_kills\", \"value\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_anbupoints\": 0, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}], \"sceneBackground\": \"ct5iZuUIk-qftU9HcpqeC\", \"sceneCharacters\": []}', '1', '2025-07-11 14:21:47.531', '2025-07-11 14:21:47.531', NULL, NULL, '1', '100', NULL, '5', '1', NULL, 'none', 'NONE', 'NONE', NULL),
