	('A-MwXj8Ik7qcMSpwv70ag', 'Aery - The Crystal Dragon', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJ1pYvfC6bo95WClq4K0wxZUmJcvThgdVenO3P', '<h1>🚨 EMERGENCY DISPATCH</h1>\n<h2>PRIORITY: S-CLASS THREAT — IMMEDIATE RESPONSE REQUIRED</h2>\n\n<p><strong>ATTENTION:</strong> All <strong>Kage-Level Shinobi (Level 80+)</strong></p>\n\n<h3>🛑 SUBJECT: Legendary Entity Manifestation</h3>\n<p><strong>Designation:</strong> <span style=\"color:deepskyblue;\">AERY, THE CRYSTAL DRAGON</span></p>\n\n<h3>📍 LOCATION</h3>\n<p>\n  Epicenter: <strong>Heart of the Shifting Sands</strong><br>\n  Sector: <strong>72</strong> — Coordinates: <strong>(10, 10)</strong><br>\n  <strong>Effect Radius:</strong> Rapidly expanding\n</p>\n\n<h3>🧱 VISUAL DESCRIPTION</h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Composition:</strong> Entirely made of semi-translucent, diamond-like crystal. Its body is angular, with geometrically flawless features.</li>\n  <li><strong>Size:</strong> Majestic and slender, notably smaller than the Emerald Dragon. Its movements are precise and eerily silent.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3>🎯 WEAKNESS</h3>\n<p>Reports indicate vulnerability to <strong>long-range weapons</strong>. Shinobi specializing in ranged combat are advised to engage from a distance.</p>\n', 'Seichi is saved once more. ', 'D', '80', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 50000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 1000000, \"reward_badges\": [\"zFcUSxAE04UDpI1ernEHL\"], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 10000, \"reward_prestige\": 10000, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 10000, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"reward_seichi_silver\": 5, \"reward_medical_experience\": 300}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"Zx2Br\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"EMERALD DRAGON.LOCATION: Last Confirmed visual contact over the Windswept Grasslands, . Currently moving slowly south towards the Shifting Sands.Sector 66, coordinates (10, 10)\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"To the Dragon\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"a_uKb\"}, {\"text\": \"Nevermind\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"uLc3x\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, {\"id\": \"a_uKb\", \"task\": \"defeat_opponents\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJtwfF6dUYJDfpFXWm3nrcPluEtIZqyLkaSV1j\", \"sector\": 72, \"latitude\": 10, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 10, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"\", \"opponentAIs\": [{\"ids\": [\"dpp9mShY4DbLT5Ae58SCf\"], \"number\": 1}], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"failObjectiveId\": \"uLc3x\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fled from the opponent\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"XqMrk\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"reward_reputation\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"reward_seichi_silver\": 0, \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": false, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false, \"reward_medical_experience\": 0}, {\"id\": \"uLc3x\", \"task\": \"fail_quest\", \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"\", \"reward_rank