	('WQsCL2aW1rDk3KWhh929J', 'The Element That Should Not Be', 'https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJCuNA6E26OYrIJuNP1pvSyz29edFtKbngjRcA', 'The thing sealed before Seichi\'s founding—the \"Fifth Element,\" also called the Void Flame or Null Chakra—was never truly destroyed. Your actions in restoring the elemental balance have inadvertently cracked its ancient bindings. The final seal, an array designed by the first Kage of all five nations, is failing. You must travel to the heart of the world and confront this anomaly before it consumes everything.\n', 'You slam the final seal into place. The Void Flame screams and vanishes. The tremors across Seichi cease, and the agonized cries of the elemental spirits fall silent. You have saved the world as it is, preserving the delicate balance at great cost. The Fifth Element sleeps again. For now.\n', 'D', '1', NULL, 'story', '{\"reward\": {\"reward_exp\": 10000, \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 75000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 1000, \"reward_prestige\": 1000, \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 1000}, \"objectives\": [{\"id\": \"LUKkG\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"attackers\": [], \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"(A powerful, multi-layered voice echoes in your mind) \\\"You who balanced the blades... you have touched the Great Seal. Your actions have weakened the cage. The Element That Should Not Be... the Void... awakens. The Heart of Balance, the very center of our world, is breaking. Go there. Face what we could only contain. The fate of Seichi is no longer in the hands of the past, but in yours.\\\"\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"\\\"I will face this threat.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"8QFzL\"}, {\"text\": \"This power is beyond me.\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"kF5Qx\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"ct5iZuUIk-qftU9HcpqeC\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"8QFzL\", \"task\": \"move_to_location\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJCuNA6E26OYrIJuNP1pvSyz29edFtKbngjRcA\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"completed\": 0, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"sectorList\": [], \"sectorType\": \"specific\", \"description\": \"Travel to the Heart of Balance, a hidden, forgotten altar at the absolute center of Seichi.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"hideLocation\": false, \"locationType\": \"specific\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": \"uGMOB\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"fhjR3i5ZEm0RR-QY9pBb4\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"uGMOB\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You arrive to find a scene of cosmic horror. The central sealing altar is shattered. The agonizing ghosts of all elements swirl around you. From the cracks in the seal, five corrupted figures rise, their forms flickering with elemental power but unified by a terrifying emptiness. They are the Echoes of the original Blade wielders, twisted by the Void.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Start Battle\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"IFbSb\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"fhjR3i5ZEm0RR-QY9pBb4\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"IFbSb\", \"task\": \"start_battle\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"\", \"opponentAIs\": [{\"ids\": [\"fwPUl3pFsc2eEe5qOcUk8\"], \"number\": 1}, {\"ids\": [\"GaI80R7Ldfle7Xw4GOgXw\"], \"number\": 1}, {\"ids\": [\"rrsVlt35Gy2Wia87E1I5g\"], \"number\": 1}, {\"ids\": [\"uMIbK4xDzhtiMtbhqFYoM\"], \"number\": 1}], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fled from the opponent\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"B-sUf\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": true}, {\"id\": \"B-sUf\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The five spirits shatter, but their chakra does not dissipate. Instead, it splinters and is drawn back together, coalescing into a single, silent flame of pure blackness. This is the core of the anomaly. Use the Ouro Sealing Crystal to contain it!\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Pick up Ouro Sealing Crystal\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"_Oi4V\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"DGYVpVSb4qFzIyY1AbLIM\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"_Oi4V\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The black flame enters the crystal, and a psychic scream of pure rage and silence assaults your mind. The crystal cracks, unable to hold the power. The Void erupts from the broken seal below!\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"Enter Combat\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"1IoOz\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"-2H-3ZFLJrfiZ46yU9DuW\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"1IoOz\", \"task\": \"start_battle\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"scaleGains\": 1, \"description\": \"\", \"opponentAIs\": [{\"ids\": [\"-QvAUrUMI0K76iUf648i5\"], \"number\": 2}], \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"drawDescription\": \"The battle ended in a draw\", \"failDescription\": \"You failed to defeat the opponent\", \"fleeDescription\": \"You fled from the opponent\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"L3V1_\", \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"completionOutcome\": \"Win\", \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"opponent_scaled_to_user\": true}, {\"id\": \"L3V1_\", \"task\": \"dialog\", \"image\": \"https://ui0arpl8sm.ufs.sh/f/Hzww9EQvYURJpIn7vsbKBAOsGCHyl3Sk0mZFrgWPUdjMJ75D\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"attackers\": [], \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You force the Null Avatar back into the chasm, but the victory is hollow. The Great Seal is actively resisting your efforts to close it, its power source now fighting back. The raw Void Flame, freed from the crystal, hovers before you. You cannot destroy it. You can only choose its fate... and yours.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"nextObjectiveId\": [{\"text\": \"The world needs balance, not another monster. I will re-seal it!\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"6tw_m\"}, {\"text\": \"The Power is Yours!\", \"nextObjectiveId\": \"FLK9d\"}], \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"-2H-3ZFLJrfiZ46yU9DuW\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"3mdVDAy9Dk23zWqfpaCpJ\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\", \"attackers_scale_gains\": 1, \"attackers_scaled_to_user\": false}, {\"id\": \"6tw_m\", \"task\": \"win_quest\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 10000, \"description\": \"You pour your chakra into the ancient array, forcing the Void Flame back into its prison. The world stabilizes\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 10000, \"reward_prestige\": 10000, \"sceneBackground\": \"-2H-3ZFLJrfiZ46yU9DuW\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\"}, {\"id\": \"FLK9d\", \"task\": \"win_quest\", \"sector\": 99, \"latitude\": 5, \"longitude\": 5, \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"You reach out and let the silent, black flame merge with your very being. The power is immense, terrifying, yours....Until nothing the power vanishes into thin air.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 10000, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"-2H-3ZFLJrfiZ46yU9DuW\", \"sceneCharacters\": [\"3mdVDAy9Dk23zWqfpaCpJ\"], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\"}, {\"id\": \"kF5Qx\", \"task\": \"fail_quest\", \"reward_exp\": 0, \"description\": \"The Null Avatar overwhelms you. With the last defender gone, the final seal shatters completely. A wave of silent, colorless energy erupts from the Heart of Balance, erasing all chakra it touches. The elements themselves begin to decay. Seichi is unmade.\", \"reward_rank\": \"NONE\", \"reward_items\": [], \"reward_money\": 0, \"reward_badges\": [], \"reward_jutsus\": [], \"reward_tokens\": 0, \"reward_prestige\": 0, \"sceneBackground\": \"ct5iZuUIk-qftU9HcpqeC\", \"sceneCharacters\": [], \"reward_bloodlines\": [], \"reward_clanpoints\": 0, \"successDescription\": \"\"}], \"sceneBackground\": \"\", \"sceneCharacters\": []}', '0', '2025-06-22 17:56:21.126', '2025-06-22 17:56:21.126', NULL, NULL, '1', '100', '0mCYDsFmXwDLwZPOta80M', '2', '1', NULL, 'none', 'NONE', 'NONE', NULL),
